font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/lena-rios-ep.jpg\" style=\"font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\"><img id=\"i-3696\" class=\"size-full wp-image\" src=\"https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/lena-rios-ep.jpg?w=650\" alt=\"Imagem\" srcset=\"https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/lena-rios-ep.jpg?w=650 650w, https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/lena-rios-ep.jpg?w=150 150w, https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/lena-rios-ep.jpg?w=300 300w, https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/lena-rios-ep.jpg?w=768 768w, https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/lena-rios-ep.jpg?w=1021 1021w, https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/lena-rios-ep.jpg 1198w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; height: auto; max-width: 100%;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">A.1. GARANTO&nbsp;</span>(Luiz Melodia/Célio José)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">A.2. EU SOU EU, NICURI É O DIABO&nbsp;</span>(Raul Seixas)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">B.1 VERÃO ESTRELADO&nbsp;</span>(Hyldon/Mazzola)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">B.2. SEM ESSA, ARANHA!&nbsp;</span>(Torquato Neto/Carlos Galvão)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Philips EP nº 6245 020</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Mais 2 faixas bônus</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">06 –&nbsp;&nbsp;Revendo Amigos (Jards Macalé / Waly Salomão) da Trila sonora da novela Tempo de viver – TP Tupi 1970</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">07- Olhar de Nanã (Edil Pacheco/Eustáquio de Oliveira) do LP De tudo um pouco&nbsp;1976 CBS</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">08 – Chapada do corisco (Torquato Neto/ Carlos Pinto) do compacto CBS de 1978</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Influenciada pelo Tropicalismo no início da década de 70, surgiu cantando composições de Jard’s Macalé e Waly Salomão e ainda composições da dupla Carlos Pinto e Torquato Neto.</p></div><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Torquato Neto conseguiu que Lena Rios se apresentasse nas casas noturnas mais badaladas do Rio de Janeiro, acompanhada por Luís Moreno (Terço), Sérgio Magrão (Terço e 14 Bis) e Renato Piau.</div><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Em 1970, pelas mãos do Torquato Neto, que a recomendou ao produtor Roberto Menescal, foi contratada pela Philips.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Em 1972, saiu, pela Philips, o compacto duplo Sem Essa Aranha, com um rock até então inédito de Raul Seixas, defendida por Lena Rios &amp; Os Lobos no VII Festival Internacional Da Canção (FIC), de 1972, “Eu Sou Eu Nicurí é o Diabo”, um blue de Luiz Melodia “Garanto”, uma de Hyldon/Mazzola “Verão Estrelado” e um rock do inesquecível Torquato Neto com Carlos Galvão “Sem Essa, Aranha”.<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.75em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></p><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Produção de Roberto Menescal e Mazzola…</div><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></div><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a href=\"https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/img.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); transition: all 0.2s ease 0s;\"><img id=\"i-3699\" class=\"size-full wp-image\" src=\"https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/img.jpg?w=490\" alt=\"Imagem\" srcset=\"https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/img.jpg?w=490 490w, https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/img.jpg?w=300 300w, https://woodstocksound.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/img.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px\" style=\"box-sizing: 